### 4. Controller Pattern

**⚠️ CRITICAL**: Business logic that doesn't belong in state management goes in controllers

Controllers are located in `lib/presentation/controllers/` and handle complex business logic:

```dart
// lib/presentation/controllers/{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_form_submission_controller.dart

/// Controller for {{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}} form submission with strategy pattern
/// Following SRP: Only handles submission logic, not form state
class {{PRIMARY_ENTITY}}FormSubmissionController {
  final SubmissionStrategy addStrategy;
  final SubmissionStrategy updateStrategy;

  {{PRIMARY_ENTITY}}FormSubmissionController({
    required this.addStrategy,
    required this.updateStrategy,
  });

  Future<Either<Failure, {{PRIMARY_ENTITY}}Entity>> submit({
    required {{PRIMARY_ENTITY}}FormState formState,
    required {{PRIMARY_ENTITY}}Entity? existing{{PRIMARY_ENTITY}},
  }) {
    final strategy = existing{{PRIMARY_ENTITY}} == null ? addStrategy : updateStrategy;
    return strategy.execute(formState, existing{{PRIMARY_ENTITY}});
  }
}
```

**Available Controllers**:
- `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_delete_controller.dart` - Deletion logic
- `receipt_scanning_controller.dart` - OCR coordination
- `{{SECONDARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_management_controller.dart` - {{SECONDARY_ENTITY}} management
- `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_form_submission_controller.dart` - Form submission with strategy pattern
- `{{PRIMARY_ENTITY_LOWER}}_scan_result_controller.dart` - Scan result processing

